WEBVTT

01:37.890 --> 01:41.030
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.920
[Episode 5]

01:47.430 --> 01:48.509
Don't be angry.

01:48.509 --> 01:50.000
It's just a job.

01:50.310 --> 01:51.560
If Yuhua doesn't want you,

01:51.560 --> 01:52.789
that's because of their poor judgment.

01:52.789 --> 01:54.250
It's not your fault at all.

01:54.759 --> 01:56.020
Don't blame yourself.

01:57.920 --> 01:59.720
Stop being angry with yourself.

02:01.170 --> 02:01.900
Hang it here.

02:09.300 --> 02:10.250
What's this?

02:10.400 --> 02:11.000
Well...

02:11.000 --> 02:12.060
This... This is...

02:13.240 --> 02:13.710
Well...

02:14.960 --> 02:16.000
If I knew this would happen,

02:16.000 --> 02:17.840
I shouldn't have forced you at that time.

02:17.840 --> 02:18.590
Anyway,

02:19.000 --> 02:21.120
I'm actually the one
who hurts myself and others.

02:21.120 --> 02:21.560
Right?

02:21.560 --> 02:22.360
I'm so contemptible, too.

02:22.360 --> 02:23.690
Everything is my fault.

02:23.910 --> 02:24.870
I'll go back and figure out a way myself.

02:24.870 --> 02:25.440
Alright.

02:25.630 --> 02:26.360
Listen to me.

02:26.750 --> 02:27.870
Let me explain.

02:28.280 --> 02:28.960
Regarding that outfit,

02:28.960 --> 02:29.910
she left it here.

02:30.079 --> 02:33.210
I've been busy lately
and had no time to tidy up the place.

02:33.310 --> 02:34.000
Alright.

02:34.000 --> 02:34.770
Don't be angry. Don't be angry.

02:34.770 --> 02:35.630
Don't be angry.

02:35.750 --> 02:37.680
See if there's anything
you don't like in the house.

02:37.680 --> 02:38.510
Just throw them all away.

02:38.510 --> 02:39.090
Okay?

02:41.280 --> 02:42.560
Stop crying.

02:42.560 --> 02:43.560
Come on.

02:43.710 --> 02:44.820
Sit down.

02:44.910 --> 02:45.560
Alright.

02:45.560 --> 02:46.520
Stop crying.

02:47.190 --> 02:48.850
I've never been fired before.

02:49.030 --> 02:50.760
It's just a job, isn't it?

02:50.840 --> 02:52.030
So what if you got fired?

02:52.030 --> 02:52.800
At worst, you can just give up working,

02:52.800 --> 02:54.710
and I'll support you financially.

02:54.710 --> 02:55.829
Do you mean

02:55.910 --> 02:56.630
I can stay at home

02:56.630 --> 02:58.560
to wash dishes, cook, clean the house

02:58.560 --> 03:00.020
and serve you like Xu Miyu?

03:00.630 --> 03:01.470
That's actually not what I mean.

03:01.470 --> 03:02.560
That's not what I mean.

03:02.560 --> 03:03.820
Don't think like that.

03:04.910 --> 03:05.970
It's good if it's not like that.

03:05.970 --> 03:06.680
Let me tell you,

03:06.680 --> 03:07.560
Nie Yucheng.

03:07.710 --> 03:08.510
If I marry you,

03:08.680 --> 03:10.560
I don't want to be the second Xu Miyu.

03:10.560 --> 03:11.840
I know. I understand.

03:13.190 --> 03:14.470
Do you think this is okay?

03:14.470 --> 03:16.360
I'll go to the travel agency tomorrow

03:16.360 --> 03:18.560
to check
among all the hotels we're working with,

03:18.560 --> 03:19.910
which one is better than Yuhua,

03:19.910 --> 03:21.770
and I'll select one for you. Okay?

03:23.840 --> 03:24.970
So you're happy now?

03:26.190 --> 03:27.400
It looks like I'm doing the right thing.

03:27.400 --> 03:28.030
Alright.

03:28.630 --> 03:29.790
Don't be angry.

03:31.280 --> 03:32.800
You won't be pretty if you're angry.

03:32.800 --> 03:33.660
Don't be angry.

03:33.840 --> 03:34.700
Don't be angry.

03:35.120 --> 03:36.560
Then what are you going to do

03:36.560 --> 03:37.820
with Xu Miyu's things?

03:37.840 --> 03:39.520
I'm going to throw them all away.

03:39.520 --> 03:40.250
Is that okay?

03:41.840 --> 03:42.750
Alright.

03:46.470 --> 03:47.910
I think in terms of hotel operations,

03:47.910 --> 03:50.290
we should not only
focus on Purong's brand concept,

03:50.290 --> 03:54.340
[Purong Hotel]

03:50.400 --> 03:52.240
but also integrate this brand concept

03:52.240 --> 03:54.170
into the daily lives of our guests.

03:54.470 --> 03:57.200
Purong represents a classic style of life

03:56.810 --> 04:04.110
[Purong Hotel]

03:57.280 --> 03:59.079
and a kind of top-level dignity.

03:59.280 --> 04:01.030
But the foundation of the hotel

04:01.150 --> 04:02.680
is still to serve the guests

04:02.800 --> 04:04.800
and the people who live in this city.

04:04.800 --> 04:07.070
Therefore, the important thing

04:07.090 --> 04:08.990
is to link with current trends

04:09.360 --> 04:11.520
and promote the lifestyle
which Purong represents

04:11.520 --> 04:13.230
to more guests.

04:13.870 --> 04:14.710
For example,

04:15.000 --> 04:16.890
we can hold a street pop-up event

04:16.990 --> 04:18.680
with the theme of Purong's

04:18.680 --> 04:20.370
classic afternoon tea

04:20.630 --> 04:23.060
so that Purong can enter people's lives

04:23.120 --> 04:24.600
in a more accessible way.

04:34.000 --> 04:37.930
Could you tell me if you've had
any experience in leading a team before?

04:39.720 --> 04:41.980
Which hotel did you work for previously?

04:43.480 --> 04:44.520
At...

04:46.070 --> 04:46.800
home.

04:57.480 --> 04:58.190
Xu Miyu.

05:01.870 --> 05:03.070
Don't be frustrated.

05:03.430 --> 05:04.360
Work experience

05:05.070 --> 05:06.390
is just a prerequisite.

05:06.390 --> 05:07.190
It can't be helped.

05:07.190 --> 05:07.870
I know.

05:09.360 --> 05:11.090
Actually, you're pretty good.

05:11.390 --> 05:13.000
You understand the underlying logic

05:13.000 --> 05:14.390
and also have your own ideas.

05:14.390 --> 05:17.390
It's just that our hotel's threshold
has shut you out.

05:17.480 --> 05:19.280
Thank you for acknowledging me.

05:20.060 --> 05:20.650
Wait!

05:21.800 --> 05:24.160
If you really need a job desperately

05:24.360 --> 05:26.270
and also want to
engage in the hotel industry,

05:26.270 --> 05:28.270
you may still have a chance for that.

05:30.270 --> 05:31.510
Starting from the entry-level jobs

05:30.390 --> 05:32.610
[Purong Hotel: We welcome you]

05:32.110 --> 05:33.560
seems like a detour,

05:32.610 --> 05:35.159
[HSKP Department]

05:34.159 --> 05:35.950
but actually,
it's to take it step by step,

05:35.190 --> 05:36.710
[F&B Department]

05:36.430 --> 05:38.210
which might be more down-to-earth.

05:38.210 --> 05:39.159
What's more, our hotel

05:39.159 --> 05:40.240
has exclusively established

05:40.240 --> 05:42.560
a fast-track promotion channel
for our own employees.

05:42.560 --> 05:43.680
Entry-level attendants

05:43.680 --> 05:46.340
also have the opportunity
to become general managers.

05:46.340 --> 05:47.110
Thank you.

05:48.120 --> 05:48.980
Think about it.

05:56.680 --> 05:57.480
Hello?

05:57.680 --> 05:58.990
I'm almost there.

05:59.190 --> 06:00.600
It'll take about

06:00.900 --> 06:01.780
20 minutes.

06:16.220 --> 06:17.160
Who are you?

06:17.160 --> 06:19.530
You're going to break my door thoroughly.

06:20.040 --> 06:22.160
What exactly is your relationship

06:22.160 --> 06:23.720
with this little scoundrel surnamed Wu?

06:23.720 --> 06:25.180
H-He's my landlord.

06:26.600 --> 06:27.720
He's not your landlord!

06:27.720 --> 06:29.480
I'm your real landlord.

06:29.600 --> 06:31.600
He still owes me two months' rent.

06:31.600 --> 06:32.270
That's impossible.

06:32.270 --> 06:34.730
I just paid him
half a year's rent yesterday.

06:36.040 --> 06:37.700
I'll call him and ask about it.

06:40.340 --> 06:42.070
[Contacts]

06:42.370 --> 06:42.500
[Unknown Caller]

06:44.170 --> 06:45.310
[Unknown Caller]

06:47.040 --> 06:47.800
Hello.

06:48.040 --> 06:49.000
Is that Xu Miyu?

06:49.920 --> 06:50.780
Yes, speaking.

06:51.120 --> 06:52.750
Your installment loan
of 5,000 yuan for this month

06:52.750 --> 06:54.010
is about to be overdue.

06:54.800 --> 06:55.720
If you still don't pay,

06:55.720 --> 06:57.560
we will take extreme measures.

06:58.380 --> 06:59.390
I got it.

06:59.390 --> 07:00.600
I'll figure out a way.

07:09.270 --> 07:12.000
Ma'am, my bag is still inside.

07:12.800 --> 07:14.500
We've received your report.

07:15.800 --> 07:17.160
Go home and wait for our notice.

07:17.160 --> 07:18.130
Officer,

07:18.270 --> 07:19.800
how long will I have to wait?

07:21.070 --> 07:22.230
I still don't know

07:22.510 --> 07:23.630
when the case can be solved.

07:23.630 --> 07:25.360
We will definitely do our best.

07:25.830 --> 07:26.920
This scoundrel surnamed Wu

07:26.920 --> 07:29.240
took all my
and this young lady's money away.

07:29.240 --> 07:31.390
He also stole many of her expensive bags.

07:31.390 --> 07:32.360
Officer,

07:32.360 --> 07:34.920
you have to arrest
and punish the culprits for us.

07:34.920 --> 07:35.920
Yes, yes, yes.

07:36.360 --> 07:37.360
Please calm down.

07:37.650 --> 07:38.600
This is money,

07:38.630 --> 07:39.830
not orange peels.

07:38.720 --> 07:39.870
[Reminder of Consumer Finance Repayment]

07:39.900 --> 07:41.080
[Dear Customer:
Tomorrow is your repayment date...]

07:40.920 --> 07:41.980
Take notes of that.

07:43.600 --> 07:44.300
Don't worry.

07:44.300 --> 07:46.830
We'll definitely handle it
properly for you.

07:58.790 --> 08:00.430
[Dad]

08:14.600 --> 08:16.680
Dad, are you asleep?

08:14.730 --> 08:18.100
[Dad]

08:19.130 --> 08:19.340
[Mom: Inviting You to Voice Chat]

08:19.510 --> 08:20.030
[Mom]

08:21.360 --> 08:22.680
Hello, Mom.

08:22.880 --> 08:23.770
Miyu.

08:24.430 --> 08:26.530
Why did you call us so late at night?

08:26.880 --> 08:28.410
Your dad is already asleep.

08:30.240 --> 08:33.200
It's about the loan for our guesthouse.

08:33.730 --> 08:36.080
There's still 5,000 yuan
to pay this month.

08:36.080 --> 08:38.490
Can you ask Dad to transfer it to me
when he has time?

08:38.490 --> 08:39.240
Miyu.

08:39.750 --> 08:41.350
Did something happen to you?

08:41.600 --> 08:43.659
Why are you asking your dad for money?

08:44.630 --> 08:47.060
Well, didn't we agree before?

08:47.150 --> 08:49.230
This money was borrowed under my name,

08:49.230 --> 08:50.790
but after the guesthouse was opened,

08:50.790 --> 08:52.550
we'd use its profits to repay the loan.

08:52.550 --> 08:53.990
Dad promised me.

08:54.020 --> 08:55.620
How come you're so tactless?

08:56.050 --> 08:58.190
Xu isn't your biological father.

08:58.330 --> 09:01.310
There are things
that he can't bring himself to say.

09:01.670 --> 09:03.150
Let me tell you the truth.

09:03.800 --> 09:05.660
Since the guesthouse was opened,

09:05.790 --> 09:08.150
only a few guests have come
in dribs and drabs.

09:08.150 --> 09:09.880
There has been no profit at all.

09:09.910 --> 09:12.360
Your dad has been so worried
these few days that he can't sleep well.

09:12.360 --> 09:14.620
How would he have money to repay the loan?

09:15.500 --> 09:16.300
Let me ask you.

09:17.080 --> 09:19.390
Did Nie Yucheng refuse to pay this money?

09:19.510 --> 09:21.510
Everything was fine two months ago.

09:22.120 --> 09:24.240
Are you two still having conflicts?

09:24.670 --> 09:26.870
Couples don't hold grudges overnight.

09:26.910 --> 09:28.120
If that doesn't work,

09:28.320 --> 09:29.440
I'll go talk to him.

09:29.870 --> 09:30.600
No.

09:31.270 --> 09:32.270
Don't overthink it.

09:32.270 --> 09:33.390
It's good if it's not like that.

09:33.390 --> 09:35.120
Just give him a chance

09:35.390 --> 09:36.790
to make up for his mistakes.

09:36.790 --> 09:39.050
Ask him to treat you better in the future.

09:40.390 --> 09:42.190
I'm doing this for your own good.

09:42.390 --> 09:45.630
You've been good-tempered
with a gentle personality since childhood.

09:45.630 --> 09:47.390
I'm afraid you'll suffer losses.

09:47.390 --> 09:48.630
Got it?

09:50.720 --> 09:52.000
Rest early then.

09:53.080 --> 09:54.080
I'm hanging up.

10:05.910 --> 10:07.720
Starting from the entry-level jobs

10:07.720 --> 10:09.270
seems like a detour,

10:09.790 --> 10:12.030
but actually,
it's to take it step by step,

10:12.030 --> 10:13.390
which might be more down-to-earth.

10:13.390 --> 10:15.390
What's more,
our hotel has exclusively established

10:15.390 --> 10:17.680
a fast-track promotion channel
for our own employees.

10:17.680 --> 10:18.910
Entry-level attendants

10:18.910 --> 10:21.970
also have the opportunity
to become general managers.

10:35.970 --> 10:38.240
[Contacts]

10:38.370 --> 10:44.740
[Qiaoqi]

11:02.760 --> 11:03.240
Hello.

11:03.240 --> 11:05.570
Are you hiring attendants right now?

11:05.830 --> 11:08.030
Yes, we are.
Have you ever worked as a cleaner before?

11:08.030 --> 11:08.830
No, I haven't.

11:08.960 --> 11:10.840
But I've been a housewife for 10 years.

11:10.840 --> 11:12.480
I'm very good at tidying up rooms.

11:12.480 --> 11:14.440
What's more,
I've had an interview at Purong before.

11:14.440 --> 11:16.320
The interviewer
recommended me to apply for this job.

11:16.320 --> 11:16.850
Alright.

11:16.870 --> 11:18.050
Bring your ID card

11:18.120 --> 11:21.750
and report for duty on the B2 floor
in the staff area during working hours.

11:21.750 --> 11:24.010
Do you provide meals and accommodation?

11:24.240 --> 11:24.670
Yes, we do.

11:24.670 --> 11:25.410
We have dorms.

11:25.410 --> 11:27.000
Can I go today?

11:27.750 --> 11:28.480
Yes, you can.

11:29.670 --> 11:30.440
Okay.

11:30.630 --> 11:32.270
Then I'll report for duty today.

11:32.270 --> 11:32.670
Okay.

11:34.480 --> 11:36.900
[Purong Hotel: Staff Entrance]

12:08.030 --> 12:09.550
Don't block the way at the entrance.

12:09.550 --> 12:10.450
Step aside!

12:13.920 --> 12:14.900
Come on! This way!

12:14.900 --> 12:15.900
Be careful!

12:16.080 --> 12:17.140
Come on! Watch out!

12:17.150 --> 12:18.200
Come on! Let's go!

12:18.240 --> 12:19.200
Make way, please!

12:19.200 --> 12:20.240
Come on! This way!

12:21.750 --> 12:22.670
Come on! Step aside!

12:22.670 --> 12:23.390
Hurry up!

12:34.870 --> 12:36.200
Are you a newcomer here?

12:38.510 --> 12:39.150
Yes.

12:39.320 --> 12:40.400
My name's Xu Miyu.

12:42.840 --> 12:43.570
Come on. Follow me.

12:43.570 --> 12:45.430
The forewoman is waiting for you.

12:52.080 --> 12:53.840
Ms. Zhang! Ms. Zhang!

12:55.840 --> 12:56.440
Go ahead.

12:57.150 --> 13:00.150
The guest in Room 1821
wants to change to another room.

13:00.820 --> 13:02.260
It's that Black Card Ji again.

13:02.260 --> 13:03.990
Let him stay wherever he wants.

13:05.120 --> 13:07.050
But we are short-handed right now.

13:08.870 --> 13:10.120
I'll ask someone to clean the room.

13:10.120 --> 13:12.320
You guys should go handle the guest now.

13:13.360 --> 13:14.440
Madam Cailu!

13:15.550 --> 13:16.480
Are you in there?

13:16.480 --> 13:17.200
Who is it?

13:17.460 --> 13:18.460
It's me.

13:19.550 --> 13:21.080
Well, what are you doing here?

13:21.080 --> 13:23.080
I brought the newcomer here for you.

13:24.720 --> 13:25.550
It's dusty here.

13:25.550 --> 13:26.680
Let's talk outside.

13:35.320 --> 13:36.270
Let me introduce myself.

13:36.270 --> 13:37.390
My name's Zhang Cailu.

13:37.390 --> 13:39.720
I'm the forewoman of the executive floor.

13:41.150 --> 13:42.150
Hello, Ms. Zhang.

13:42.240 --> 13:43.270
I'm Xu Miyu.

13:44.030 --> 13:45.490
Your hands are quite soft.

13:46.480 --> 13:48.340
You've never worked before, huh?

13:50.150 --> 13:51.510
I've done housework at home.

13:51.510 --> 13:53.200
You are 35 years old now.

13:54.910 --> 13:56.040
Age is not a problem.

13:56.120 --> 13:56.980
Take your time.

13:57.870 --> 13:58.720
Yin Xiang.

13:58.720 --> 13:59.850
Where are you going?

14:01.510 --> 14:02.750
Take Miyu upstairs

14:03.090 --> 14:04.810
and clean Room 1821.

14:05.750 --> 14:07.150
Consider it as training.

14:08.750 --> 14:09.720
Don't you want the training allowance?

14:09.720 --> 14:10.250
Yes, I do!

14:16.330 --> 14:17.640
This way. That room.

14:20.510 --> 14:21.570
The room at the end.

14:27.690 --> 14:29.090
Just leave the cart here.

14:35.200 --> 14:36.630
Take the vacuum cleaner with you.

14:36.630 --> 14:37.260
The vacuum cleaner.

14:37.260 --> 14:37.720
Okay.

14:44.890 --> 14:47.030
Luckily,
it's not an extremely messy scene.

14:47.030 --> 14:48.030
Let me tell you.

14:48.030 --> 14:49.630
Opening a hotel room door

14:49.630 --> 14:50.890
is like opening a blind box.

14:50.890 --> 14:51.670
You'll never know

14:51.670 --> 14:53.510
what kind of mess the guests left inside.

14:53.510 --> 14:55.480
A couple of days ago, a woman came here

14:55.480 --> 14:58.110
and gorged on seafood and alcohol
in her room.

14:58.140 --> 14:58.840
You have no idea

14:58.840 --> 15:00.640
how messy she made the room look.

15:03.770 --> 15:04.690
Is that so?

15:17.480 --> 15:18.270
Mr. Ji,

15:18.400 --> 15:19.460
please have a rest.

15:20.270 --> 15:21.120
Thank you.

16:12.800 --> 16:15.750
[Shampoo]

16:22.050 --> 16:22.550
Hello.

16:22.570 --> 16:23.970
Hello. How can I help...

16:25.010 --> 16:26.810
I want to change to another room.

16:38.240 --> 16:39.490
Make this flush.

16:39.670 --> 16:40.350
Okay.

16:40.370 --> 16:41.370
Then fold it down.

16:45.690 --> 16:47.200
Fold this inside,

16:47.200 --> 16:48.300
leaving a corner.

16:49.390 --> 16:50.030
Like this.

16:53.170 --> 16:54.430
Then lift this back up.

17:27.720 --> 17:28.510
Watch carefully.

17:28.349 --> 17:31.360
[Hairdryer Bag]

17:28.610 --> 17:29.540
The hairdryer,

17:30.640 --> 17:31.310
shower caps,

17:31.310 --> 17:32.030
nail files,

17:32.030 --> 17:32.770
hair ties,

17:33.400 --> 17:34.110
toothbrushes,

17:34.110 --> 17:34.750
combs

17:34.830 --> 17:36.360
and hand cream are all here.

17:36.440 --> 17:38.160
Soap. Remember all of this.

17:38.510 --> 17:39.400
If the left-and-right order

17:39.400 --> 17:41.030
of these items in the drawer is wrong,

17:41.030 --> 17:42.160
you'll get scolded.

17:43.640 --> 17:44.810
Replenish two toothbrushes.

17:44.810 --> 17:45.420
Coming.

17:47.610 --> 17:48.410
One is enough.

17:52.530 --> 17:53.990
This hand cream is used up.

17:54.410 --> 17:56.140
Replenish a tube of handcream.

17:57.640 --> 17:58.360
Yin Xiang,

17:58.380 --> 18:00.330
clean up Room 1813.

18:01.270 --> 18:02.510
Why is there another room?

18:02.510 --> 18:04.030
Isn't Room 1813 empty?

18:04.030 --> 18:05.400
The guest in Room 1812 changed to it.

18:05.400 --> 18:06.550
Now he wants a change again.

18:06.550 --> 18:07.310
Copy that.

18:08.080 --> 18:08.960
This kind of guest

18:08.960 --> 18:09.920
is the hardest to deal with.

18:09.920 --> 18:11.240
If you don't
meet their expectations even slightly,

18:11.240 --> 18:12.960
they will give you a bad review.

18:12.960 --> 18:13.590
Oh, by the way,

18:13.590 --> 18:14.750
you have to be careful from now on.

18:14.750 --> 18:17.070
Getting three bad reviews
means you will be fired.

18:17.070 --> 18:17.790
Let's go.

18:26.650 --> 18:28.100
Hello, room service.

18:38.120 --> 18:39.620
Hello, room service.

18:53.250 --> 18:54.450
Hello, room service.

19:06.680 --> 19:07.880
Hello, room service.

19:12.070 --> 19:15.550
It can't be helped. The guest complained,
so we have to clean it again.

19:15.550 --> 19:16.720
A bit further there... further back.

19:16.720 --> 19:17.760
Wipe the right side again.

19:17.760 --> 19:18.200
Here?

19:18.260 --> 19:19.120
The right. Yes.

19:20.830 --> 19:22.960
It's almost done. Clean the tea table.

19:41.830 --> 19:42.870
Yin Xiang! Yin Xiang!

19:42.870 --> 19:43.730
Let me tell you.

19:44.960 --> 19:46.810
He's so handsome. Super handsome.

19:46.810 --> 19:48.410
That incredible jawline.

19:48.510 --> 19:49.690
So handsome.

19:50.550 --> 19:51.310
A newcomer?

19:52.070 --> 19:52.930
My apprentice.

19:53.160 --> 19:54.660
Miyu, this is...

19:54.680 --> 19:55.370
Ke Wenxue.

19:55.680 --> 19:56.590
Hello, my name's Xu Miyu.

19:56.590 --> 19:57.350
Hello.

19:58.070 --> 19:59.960
How come I feel
you look a bit familiar to me?

19:59.960 --> 20:01.860
How come I feel I've seen you somewhere?

20:01.860 --> 20:02.880
Have we met before?

20:02.880 --> 20:04.680
Everyone looks familiar to you.

20:04.790 --> 20:06.200
Let's go. It's time to be off work.

20:06.200 --> 20:08.030
If we don't get off work now, the guest
might want to change rooms again later.

20:08.030 --> 20:08.560
This way.

20:11.270 --> 20:13.350
I just feel like I've seen her before.

20:26.150 --> 20:26.880
Miyu,

20:26.910 --> 20:28.250
this is your dorm.

20:29.200 --> 20:30.330
Remember this door.

20:31.090 --> 20:32.490
You can sleep on this bed.

20:34.230 --> 20:35.270
Thank you, Ms. Zhang.

20:35.270 --> 20:36.200
You're welcome.

20:36.270 --> 20:36.880
Rest early.

20:36.880 --> 20:37.810
I'm leaving now.

20:38.400 --> 20:38.880
Okay.

21:37.470 --> 21:38.530
It's true, huh?

21:38.960 --> 21:40.760
It really costs over 2,000 yuan.

21:41.550 --> 21:42.920
Well, if she's using
such an expensive suitcase,

21:42.920 --> 21:45.120
why is she working here as an attendant?

21:45.240 --> 21:46.640
Maybe she went bankrupt.

21:47.610 --> 21:50.270
Otherwise,
maybe she was dumped by her husband.

21:50.400 --> 21:52.380
Look. She's so much older than us.

21:52.410 --> 21:54.340
She must have been married before.

21:54.510 --> 21:56.990
Also look at her figure and temperament.

21:57.440 --> 21:59.720
When Yin Xiang walked with her
during the daytime today,

21:59.720 --> 22:01.760
she looked like a little maid.

22:01.790 --> 22:02.790
This is really crazy.

22:02.790 --> 22:06.520
Even the middle class is coming to
compete with us in this industry.

22:07.270 --> 22:07.950
Sit.

22:10.310 --> 22:12.920
♪ Face the wind ♪

22:13.480 --> 22:15.350
♪ Defeat the wind ♪

22:15.590 --> 22:16.370
Be quiet!

22:17.070 --> 22:20.790
♪ If time could be slower ♪

22:21.000 --> 22:24.000
-♪ I'll be closer to expectations ♪
-I'm taking listening tests.

22:24.000 --> 22:25.590
Can you keep your voice down?

22:25.590 --> 22:27.030
Ms. Luo,

22:27.030 --> 22:29.350
this is a dorm, not a classroom.

22:29.350 --> 22:31.510
If you think this is noisy,
go to the study room.

22:31.510 --> 22:32.640
How ill-mannered.

22:45.710 --> 22:46.640
Although I was tired today,

22:46.640 --> 22:48.640
at least, I got to see a handsome guy.

22:48.900 --> 22:50.270
You enjoyed looking at the handsome guy

22:50.270 --> 22:52.000
while we were exhausted today.

22:52.550 --> 22:53.750
Keep your voice down.

22:56.000 --> 22:56.960
I remember now.

22:56.960 --> 22:58.030
The newcomer who came today

22:58.030 --> 23:00.440
was that rich woman
who ate and drank a lot

23:00.550 --> 23:02.260
alone in Room 1816 that day.

23:02.530 --> 23:03.960
Why did she come here?

24:01.240 --> 24:02.750
I couldn't have made a mistake.

24:02.750 --> 24:05.960
If there was a mistake, the receptionists
must have assigned them wrongly.

24:05.960 --> 24:06.590
Now that a mistake has been made,

24:06.590 --> 24:07.680
switch them back at once.

24:07.680 --> 24:09.030
I'm busy right now.

24:09.030 --> 24:10.240
I still have a pile
of guests' dry-cleaned clothes to fold.

24:10.240 --> 24:10.880
Miyu.

24:11.510 --> 24:12.790
You're here just in time.

24:12.790 --> 24:14.750
Yin Xiang
mixed up the takeout for two rooms.

24:14.750 --> 24:16.200
The lobby clerks mixed them up.

24:16.200 --> 24:16.930
Do me a favor.

24:17.030 --> 24:18.110
Make adjustments between the two sides.

24:18.110 --> 24:20.840
If the guests need anything,
try to satisfy them.

24:20.960 --> 24:22.290
Go fold the clothes now.

24:22.830 --> 24:23.960
Thank you both.

24:26.680 --> 24:27.880
Thanks for your help.

24:33.960 --> 24:35.140
I'm sorry, sir.

24:35.170 --> 24:36.310
We made a mistake just now.

24:36.310 --> 24:38.110
I'm here to switch your takeout.

24:39.030 --> 24:39.680
Okay.

24:41.000 --> 24:42.030
Room service.

24:44.510 --> 24:45.070
I'm sorry, sir.

24:45.070 --> 24:47.930
-I'm here to switch your take-
-This is outrageous.

24:51.830 --> 24:53.960
How come it's you?

24:55.210 --> 24:57.020
You are...

25:22.070 --> 25:23.200
I sincerely apologize.

25:23.200 --> 25:24.820
This is our oversight.

25:24.920 --> 25:27.000
It was caused
by our staff's careless cleaning.

25:27.000 --> 25:28.790
We'll definitely deal with this seriously.

25:28.790 --> 25:29.510
However, regarding this matter,

25:29.510 --> 25:31.020
we've already investigated it thoroughly.

25:31.020 --> 25:33.530
It's entirely our hotel's responsibility,

25:33.800 --> 25:35.660
so you can rest assured, Mrs. Nie.

25:43.550 --> 25:44.310
Miyu,

25:44.420 --> 25:46.020
how is the adjustment going?

25:47.000 --> 25:47.750
I...

25:47.750 --> 25:48.480
I haven't...

25:48.500 --> 25:49.360
How about this?

25:49.550 --> 25:50.440
The guest in Room 1822

25:50.440 --> 25:52.290
has already ordered
at the Chinese restaurant.

25:52.290 --> 25:53.960
Now the key is that the guest in Room 1812

25:53.960 --> 25:55.690
is a bit difficult to deal with.

25:55.820 --> 25:56.990
I will go talk to him.

25:57.920 --> 25:58.780
I can handle it.

26:15.760 --> 26:17.740
[Do Not Disturb]

26:36.360 --> 26:38.850
Now that's all
for the takeout incident from last night.

26:38.850 --> 26:40.160
Luckily, the guests let it slide.

26:40.160 --> 26:41.220
Let's just move on.

26:41.720 --> 26:42.520
Luo Qingping,

26:42.680 --> 26:44.680
you are in charge of Room 1812 today.

26:45.240 --> 26:46.700
I'm not going to Room 1812.

26:47.080 --> 26:48.720
Are you afraid of getting a bad review?

26:48.720 --> 26:49.460
Aren't you afraid of that?

26:49.460 --> 26:50.550
If not, you can go.

26:50.680 --> 26:51.570
I've been there.

26:51.570 --> 26:52.770
We've all been there.

26:52.770 --> 26:53.600
You are the only one who hasn't.

26:53.600 --> 26:54.810
Alright.

26:54.830 --> 26:56.000
Stop arguing, everyone.

26:56.000 --> 26:57.200
Let's take turns.

26:57.440 --> 26:58.240
Luo Qingping,

26:58.380 --> 27:00.640
you're the most capable one on our floor.

27:00.720 --> 27:01.750
Go show him what you can do

27:01.750 --> 27:03.000
so that he can't find any fault with it.

27:03.000 --> 27:05.160
Even the most capable person
shouldn't be treated like this, huh?

27:05.160 --> 27:07.350
Last time, I was also the one
who handled the weirdo

27:07.350 --> 27:08.350
who wanted his socks to be hand-washed.

27:08.350 --> 27:09.280
And before that,

27:09.480 --> 27:11.160
that family of five with three sons

27:11.160 --> 27:12.830
was served by me
from beginning to end, too.

27:12.830 --> 27:16.160
Madam Cailu, you just can't
cherish elites in this way, huh?

27:23.850 --> 27:24.450
I'll go.

27:31.790 --> 27:34.920
Hello, I'm the attendant
for the room cleaning service.

27:35.270 --> 27:37.200
Hello, I'm Xu Miyu
from the HSKP Department.

27:37.200 --> 27:38.720
I'm responsible
for cleaning your room today.

27:38.720 --> 27:39.880
May I come in?

27:40.720 --> 27:41.590
Yes.

28:12.750 --> 28:14.030
Are you going to stand here

28:14.030 --> 28:15.310
to supervise my work?

28:40.720 --> 28:41.590
Mr. Ji.

28:41.590 --> 28:43.990
Do you need me
to change the bedding for you?

28:44.940 --> 28:46.400
You can decide. Thank you.

28:52.070 --> 28:52.600
Alright.

28:53.020 --> 28:53.760
It's not necessary. Thanks.

28:53.760 --> 28:55.290
You don't need to change it.

28:55.970 --> 28:57.020
That's not okay.

28:58.160 --> 28:59.500
I have to help you

28:59.530 --> 29:00.790
change it thoroughly,

29:00.850 --> 29:02.140
from top to bottom,

29:02.170 --> 29:03.420
from left to right

29:03.440 --> 29:04.850
and from the inside to the outside.

29:04.850 --> 29:05.740
Otherwise,

29:05.950 --> 29:07.320
if the previous guest

29:07.440 --> 29:09.160
left something indecent here

29:09.180 --> 29:10.580
and you want to blame it on me,

29:10.580 --> 29:12.180
I won't be able to explain it.

29:27.660 --> 29:28.560
Mr. Ji,

29:28.880 --> 29:30.640
are you always such a helpful man?

29:30.640 --> 29:31.830
Whenever you see someone in trouble,

29:31.830 --> 29:34.110
you just can't help lending a hand.

29:34.370 --> 29:36.200
Even if it means
covering up scandals for others,

29:36.200 --> 29:38.060
you still won't hesitate to do it.

29:38.600 --> 29:40.010
Why are you here,

29:40.560 --> 29:41.200
Mrs. Nie?

29:41.200 --> 29:42.200
Thanks to you,

29:42.790 --> 29:44.310
I am no longer Mrs. Nie now.

29:46.820 --> 29:47.560
I...

29:48.060 --> 29:51.260
I think there might be some
misunderstanding between us.

29:51.320 --> 29:52.980
Is there a misunderstanding?

29:54.200 --> 29:57.060
You helped my ex-husband
lie to me last time.

29:57.200 --> 29:59.200
Have you forgotten that so quickly?

30:00.590 --> 30:02.110
If my previous service

30:02.350 --> 30:04.160
caused you any unpleasant experience,

30:04.160 --> 30:06.920
I sincerely apologize to you.

30:08.800 --> 30:10.820
But if I'm not mistaken,

30:11.160 --> 30:12.690
it's your working time now.

30:13.030 --> 30:14.550
Do the attendants at Purong Hotel

30:14.550 --> 30:16.280
all like to chat while working?

30:21.280 --> 30:22.410
I need to take a call.

30:22.530 --> 30:24.330
Take your time to clean the room.

30:25.060 --> 30:25.870
Andrew.

30:26.480 --> 30:27.240
Yeah, sure.

30:27.240 --> 30:29.700
I'm not doing
anything important right now.

30:29.920 --> 30:30.670
Go ahead.

30:40.590 --> 30:41.080
Ms. Zhang,

30:41.080 --> 30:42.220
are you looking for me?

30:42.220 --> 30:43.220
Close the door.

30:43.380 --> 30:43.940
Okay.

30:51.110 --> 30:52.510
Let me ask you something.

30:52.510 --> 30:54.200
When you cleaned

30:54.200 --> 30:55.030
Room 1812,

30:55.030 --> 30:55.960
was the guest there?

30:55.960 --> 30:56.590
Yes.

30:56.590 --> 30:57.240
Did this guest

30:57.240 --> 30:58.960
pick on you to your face

30:58.960 --> 31:00.640
and deliberately
make things difficult for you?

31:00.640 --> 31:02.160
Tell me the details

31:02.160 --> 31:03.820
so that I can warn the other girls

31:03.820 --> 31:05.050
not to get in his way.

31:05.400 --> 31:06.480
He didn't make things difficult for me.

31:06.480 --> 31:07.750
He really didn't?

31:08.430 --> 31:09.360
You have no idea

31:09.380 --> 31:12.180
how badly Jia got scolded
when she came back that day.

31:12.180 --> 31:15.180
He said it was unprofessional for her
to wear perfume.

31:15.510 --> 31:17.640
Actually, the young girl
just loved being pretty,

31:17.640 --> 31:19.440
and her perfume was a bit strong.

31:19.850 --> 31:21.380
It was as if she had stabbed him
in the nose.

31:21.380 --> 31:23.240
Then he just gave her a bad review.

31:23.750 --> 31:24.680
Did he...

31:25.640 --> 31:27.160
also give me a bad review?

31:27.830 --> 31:29.510
He didn't give you a bad review.

31:29.510 --> 31:32.120
Encountering weird guests
like Black Card Ji,

31:32.140 --> 31:33.890
we attendants tend to suffer the most.

31:33.890 --> 31:35.950
But we can only endure the suffering.

31:35.960 --> 31:39.000
So we have to share information
with each other

31:39.030 --> 31:40.240
to avoid pitfalls.

31:40.240 --> 31:41.000
Got it?

31:41.240 --> 31:42.070
Got it.

31:44.790 --> 31:45.720
Ms. Zhang,

31:46.110 --> 31:48.880
why do you all call him Black Card Ji?

31:48.900 --> 31:50.030
You don't know this?

31:50.090 --> 31:52.880
Our hotel's top-tier VIP card

31:52.960 --> 31:54.590
is a black card made of graphite.

31:54.590 --> 31:56.250
There are only three in total.

31:57.000 --> 31:59.000
And that Mr. Ji has one.

32:00.550 --> 32:01.750
This person...

32:02.430 --> 32:03.440
is that powerful?

32:03.460 --> 32:04.540
This guy

32:04.570 --> 32:06.110
definitely has a strong background.

32:06.110 --> 32:07.870
He's holding a black card

32:07.900 --> 32:09.720
and staying on our executive floor.

32:09.720 --> 32:12.030
If he says someone is good or bad,

32:12.030 --> 32:14.160
his word carries much more weight
than that of the others.

32:14.160 --> 32:15.400
You must remember

32:15.440 --> 32:16.680
not to provoke him.

32:17.810 --> 32:18.350
Ms. Zhang,

32:18.350 --> 32:19.270
the guest in Room 1815

32:19.270 --> 32:20.600
is calling for service.

32:21.510 --> 32:22.350
Copy that.

32:22.350 --> 32:23.280
Coming right up.

32:23.590 --> 32:25.020
Go to Room 1815.

32:25.160 --> 32:25.680
Okay.

32:37.200 --> 32:38.400
Can't you see that?

32:38.580 --> 32:39.870
Pick them up now!

32:40.520 --> 32:41.090
Okay.

32:52.110 --> 32:54.370
I don't even know
if you guys understand.

33:03.920 --> 33:05.120
Come on. Here you are.

33:06.120 --> 33:08.190
Are they arranged in order?

33:13.510 --> 33:14.570
Are you a newcomer?

33:15.830 --> 33:16.960
What's your name?

33:17.430 --> 33:18.950
My name is Xu Miyu.

33:21.680 --> 33:22.200
Go away.

33:22.200 --> 33:23.130
Don't bother me.

33:24.590 --> 33:25.030
Okay.

33:38.350 --> 33:39.210
Miyu.

33:39.640 --> 33:40.640
You're not the only one
that's afraid of him.

33:40.640 --> 33:41.720
We're all afraid of him.

33:41.720 --> 33:42.790
I've heard

33:42.810 --> 33:44.040
that old man is a writer.

33:44.040 --> 33:45.110
When he's in a good mood,

33:45.110 --> 33:46.200
he acts like a normal person.

33:46.200 --> 33:48.220
But when he has writer's block,
he'll just scold others.

33:48.220 --> 33:48.790
Whoever has to deal with

33:48.790 --> 33:50.240
a guy like that is just unlucky.

33:50.240 --> 33:52.350
I actually think this kind of person
is easier to get along with.

33:52.350 --> 33:53.550
They don't give bad reviews
indiscriminately.

33:53.550 --> 33:54.830
They're much better than Black Card Ji.

33:54.830 --> 33:56.830
That's easy for you to say.

33:56.920 --> 33:58.180
Why didn't you go then?

33:58.750 --> 33:59.550
Ke Wenxue.

34:00.190 --> 34:02.590
Just put all this chattering energy
into your work performance.

34:02.590 --> 34:04.930
Aren't you just so envious of me
for having no bad reviews?

34:04.930 --> 34:06.240
Let's switch rooms and you can try it.

34:06.240 --> 34:07.300
Let's switch then.

34:07.300 --> 34:08.350
Stop arguing.

34:09.400 --> 34:11.699
Let's all try not to get any bad reviews.

34:11.850 --> 34:13.510
We don't need you
to be the peacemaker here.

34:13.510 --> 34:16.280
Except me, you're the only one here
who hasn't gotten a bad review.

34:16.280 --> 34:18.440
That's just because
you haven't been here for long.

34:18.440 --> 34:20.699
Let's see how much longer you can hang in.

34:23.670 --> 34:25.330
Room 1815 needs room service.

34:29.320 --> 34:30.980
Room 1815 needs room service.

34:34.500 --> 34:35.480
I'll help you clean up later.

34:35.480 --> 34:36.440
Just go now.

34:36.880 --> 34:37.510
Coming.

34:53.719 --> 34:55.780
Don't interrupt my train of thought.

35:05.000 --> 35:06.050
Engineering Department.

35:06.050 --> 35:07.310
Is anyone there now?

35:07.430 --> 35:09.420
The light in Room 1815 is broken.

35:09.480 --> 35:10.080
Copy that.

35:12.190 --> 35:13.960
Is it this late already?

35:14.590 --> 35:15.280
Xu Miyu.

35:16.210 --> 35:17.070
Come on.

35:17.090 --> 35:19.350
Come here and take a look at this passage.

35:20.130 --> 35:20.930
Come on.

35:22.590 --> 35:24.590
Look. What do you think of this part?

35:25.590 --> 35:26.450
[He put on that ring on the wedding day.]

35:26.470 --> 35:27.240
[The wedding was simple and plain,
with no grand ceremony.]

35:27.260 --> 35:28.370
[Nor were there any romantic vows.]

35:31.360 --> 35:32.420
It's well written.

35:33.630 --> 35:35.670
Does it show

35:35.670 --> 35:37.670
the hidden pain

35:37.670 --> 35:38.930
in Tingsheng's heart?

35:39.230 --> 35:41.320
Come on. Look at that ring.

35:41.360 --> 35:43.260
I added it on purpose.

35:41.430 --> 35:42.020
[He put on that ring on the wedding day.]

35:42.040 --> 35:42.610
[The wedding was simple and plain,
with no grand ceremony.]

35:42.640 --> 35:43.340
[Nor were there any romantic vows.]

35:43.760 --> 35:45.980
I just want to make it impossible

35:46.130 --> 35:47.330
to take off that ring.

35:47.710 --> 35:49.000
Since he can't take it off,

35:49.000 --> 35:50.510
he won't be able to resist

35:50.640 --> 35:51.760
that betrothal.

35:52.840 --> 35:53.970
Isn't it wonderful?

35:54.890 --> 35:55.650
Yes, it is.

35:56.110 --> 35:58.550
With your mention of that,
I've noticed it, too.

35:58.550 --> 35:59.710
Adding the ring as a prop

35:59.710 --> 36:01.630
is such a wonderful detail.

36:02.960 --> 36:04.380
If you can even notice that,

36:04.380 --> 36:05.320
the editor

36:05.480 --> 36:07.680
can't possibly say
he's unable to notice it, huh?

36:07.680 --> 36:09.400
They will definitely notice it.

36:09.400 --> 36:10.590
If they can't notice it,

36:10.590 --> 36:11.850
they must be blind.

36:14.350 --> 36:15.160
You can leave now.

36:15.160 --> 36:16.560
No need to clean the room.

36:16.890 --> 36:18.400
I'll stay here
to wait for the Engineering Department

36:18.400 --> 36:19.600
to repair this light.

36:19.760 --> 36:21.190
Just ignore it. You may go.

36:21.190 --> 36:22.880
Is the attendant-on-duty
of the executive floor there?

36:22.880 --> 36:24.030
Room 1803 is pressing for the supper.

36:24.030 --> 36:24.710
Copy that.

36:25.230 --> 36:25.800
Alright.

36:26.040 --> 36:27.030
Good night then.

36:36.040 --> 36:36.730
Thanks.

36:39.800 --> 36:40.730
You're welcome.

37:01.480 --> 37:04.140
Sir, did you enjoy your stay
these past few days?

37:05.280 --> 37:06.550
Please sign here.

37:08.780 --> 37:09.960
Could I take a minute of your time

37:09.960 --> 37:11.920
to write a review on our HSKP Department

37:11.920 --> 37:13.030
so that it can help our hotel improve?

37:13.030 --> 37:13.840
Sure.

37:19.320 --> 37:20.000
Hello.

37:20.710 --> 37:22.150
Have you finished reading it?

37:22.150 --> 37:23.190
This time,

37:23.190 --> 37:25.030
you have to pay me extra money

37:25.550 --> 37:26.710
for the costs of rush work

37:26.710 --> 37:28.400
and supper.

37:31.110 --> 37:31.880
Wait!

37:32.630 --> 37:33.630
What did you say?

37:33.880 --> 37:36.590
I wrote for you for over half a month,

37:36.920 --> 37:38.630
and you just quit with one word?

37:38.630 --> 37:39.590
Refund?

37:39.920 --> 37:42.320
In your dreams!

37:45.810 --> 37:47.860
Why are you standing there like a log?

37:47.860 --> 37:49.990
Do you think I'm such a laughingstock?

37:50.430 --> 37:51.460
I'm sorry, sir.

37:52.000 --> 37:53.300
There was nothing to eat.

37:52.150 --> 37:54.320
[Guest Satisfaction Survey]

37:53.800 --> 37:55.530
And no one repaired the broken light.

37:55.530 --> 37:57.860
How could there be such a five-star hotel?

37:58.150 --> 38:00.740
Take it to your boss, idiot!

38:12.820 --> 38:14.680
Ms. Zhang, are you looking for me?

38:14.730 --> 38:17.550
[Xu Miyu, 18th Floor,
Morning Shift, Bad Review]

38:18.470 --> 38:20.210
When did I get a bad review?

38:20.280 --> 38:22.250
It's all because of
that grumpy old man in Room 1815.

38:22.250 --> 38:23.630
He wrote some garbage

38:23.630 --> 38:24.670
and got his draft rejected,

38:24.670 --> 38:26.400
so he vented his anger all on us.

38:26.550 --> 38:29.150
He cursed the whole hotel
from top to bottom.

38:29.320 --> 38:30.720
We're really so unlucky.

38:32.320 --> 38:33.440
But this bad review

38:34.710 --> 38:36.230
isn't directed at me.

38:37.670 --> 38:38.660
Miyu,

38:38.920 --> 38:40.330
here's the thing.

38:40.590 --> 38:41.320
Come on.

38:41.360 --> 38:42.020
Take a look.

38:42.480 --> 38:43.630
She and she...

38:44.440 --> 38:46.340
Neither of them are good enough.

38:46.920 --> 38:48.980
They can barely protect themselves.

38:49.320 --> 38:50.980
So you'll have to take the hit.

38:52.400 --> 38:54.000
I have my difficulties, too.

38:54.070 --> 38:55.670
If I get two more bad reviews,

38:57.670 --> 38:58.740
I'll be done for.

38:58.790 --> 38:59.840
Don't be nervous.

38:59.870 --> 39:01.110
Let me tell you a secret.

39:01.110 --> 39:03.080
Even if you get three bad reviews,

39:03.190 --> 39:04.590
the hotel won't fire you.

39:05.440 --> 39:06.000
Really?

39:06.000 --> 39:07.960
They'll just deduct your bonuses at most.

39:07.960 --> 39:08.760
How much?

39:08.880 --> 39:09.940
All of it, for sure.

39:09.960 --> 39:11.560
You think he'd go easy on you?

39:13.440 --> 39:14.400
Don't worry.

39:14.550 --> 39:16.150
If you get another bad review,

39:16.150 --> 39:18.550
I'll also find someone
to remove it for you.

39:18.880 --> 39:20.340
Just do each other a favor.

39:25.280 --> 39:26.280
Okay.

39:33.500 --> 39:34.950
You need to eat more.

39:35.320 --> 39:37.160
Take good care of your health.

39:37.660 --> 39:40.760
[Longevity,
Happy Birthday to My Dear Mother]

39:38.070 --> 39:39.440
Wensi Tofu.
All the dishes have been served.

39:39.440 --> 39:40.770
Please enjoy your meal.

39:43.780 --> 39:46.750
[Longevity,
Happy Birthday to My Dear Mother]

39:43.840 --> 39:45.320
To celebrate this birthday today,

39:45.320 --> 39:46.880
I'm really so happy.

39:47.480 --> 39:48.990
My son is successful in his career,

39:48.990 --> 39:51.510
and my daughter-in-law
even brought our family a grandson.

39:51.510 --> 39:53.110
I am completely content.

39:53.110 --> 39:54.070
Thank you all.

39:53.190 --> 39:57.150
[Longevity,
Happy Birthday to My Dear Mother]

39:55.320 --> 39:56.400
Mom, happy birthday.

39:56.400 --> 39:56.980
Cheers.

39:57.230 --> 39:59.090
-Happy birthday.
-Happy birthday.

39:59.090 --> 39:59.480
Thank you.

39:59.480 --> 40:00.790
I wish you good health.

40:00.920 --> 40:02.550
Thank you.

40:02.590 --> 40:04.220
How come Mom knows it's a boy?

40:06.940 --> 40:08.140
Everyone, let's eat.

40:08.460 --> 40:09.760
Please help yourselves.

40:09.760 --> 40:10.840
This Purong Hotel

40:10.840 --> 40:12.300
is indeed magnificent.

40:12.590 --> 40:15.050
I've always wanted to come in
and take a look.

40:15.150 --> 40:15.840
Thanks to you,

40:15.840 --> 40:17.750
I can do so today.

40:17.770 --> 40:18.730
Not at all.

40:19.000 --> 40:21.800
This is just a small gesture
from the younger ones.

40:23.110 --> 40:23.880
Mr. Nie.

40:24.280 --> 40:24.920
Mr. Wei.

40:25.030 --> 40:26.230
Welcome to our hotel.

40:26.400 --> 40:27.110
It's very nice of you to say that.

40:27.110 --> 40:27.920
Thank you.

40:27.960 --> 40:29.000
This room is well decorated.

40:29.000 --> 40:30.460
Thanks for your hard work.

40:30.880 --> 40:32.110
Let me make an introduction.

40:32.110 --> 40:33.910
This is the head of Purong Hotel,

40:33.950 --> 40:34.990
Mr. Wei Siyuan.

40:35.020 --> 40:36.030
Don't call me the head.

40:36.030 --> 40:36.800
I'm just the chief butler,

40:36.800 --> 40:37.880
aiming at serving everyone.

40:37.880 --> 40:38.840
What chief butler?

40:38.840 --> 40:40.040
You are just the head.

40:40.760 --> 40:41.440
Mr. Wei,

40:41.440 --> 40:42.370
nice to meet you.

40:42.630 --> 40:43.620
This is my mother.

40:43.620 --> 40:44.870
You can call me Wei.

40:45.480 --> 40:46.190
Mrs. Nie,

40:46.280 --> 40:47.030
today, it's my great honor

40:47.030 --> 40:48.360
that you can celebrate your birthday

40:48.360 --> 40:49.670
in our hotel.

40:49.710 --> 40:50.800
I have to drink a toast to you properly.

40:50.800 --> 40:51.190
Thank you.

40:51.190 --> 40:52.280
-Thank you, Mr. Wei.
-May you...

40:52.280 --> 40:54.310
Remain happy every day just like today,

40:54.310 --> 40:56.560
and stay young forever.

40:57.840 --> 40:59.340
Mr. Wei, it's very kind of you
to say that.

40:59.340 --> 41:00.190
Please drink as you prefer.

41:00.190 --> 41:00.870
Okay.

41:01.190 --> 41:01.990
Have a seat.

41:02.010 --> 41:03.410
Come on. Refill my glass.

41:04.150 --> 41:05.030
Come on, Mr. Nie.

41:05.030 --> 41:05.800
Come on.

41:05.800 --> 41:06.550
Let me drink a toast to you individually.

41:06.550 --> 41:07.360
Come on.

41:07.800 --> 41:08.480
Thank you.

41:08.480 --> 41:09.550
Mr. Nie here

41:09.550 --> 41:10.710
is a true winner in life.

41:10.710 --> 41:11.670
He really deserves this reputation.

41:11.670 --> 41:12.880
Thanks for your kind words.

41:12.880 --> 41:14.540
Let's move forward together.

41:14.800 --> 41:15.440
Let's move forward together.

41:15.440 --> 41:16.280
Cheers.

41:18.710 --> 41:20.280
Alright. Since this is a family feast,

41:20.280 --> 41:22.000
I won't disturb you any longer.

41:22.000 --> 41:22.630
Please forgive us

41:22.630 --> 41:23.920
if there's any oversight in our service.

41:23.920 --> 41:25.410
Kaixin,
stay here and take good care of them.

41:25.410 --> 41:25.760
Okay.

41:25.760 --> 41:26.760
Please enjoy your meal.

41:26.760 --> 41:27.690
I'm leaving now.

41:28.400 --> 41:29.600
Mom, I'll see him out.

41:30.840 --> 41:31.670
Mr. Wei.

41:33.070 --> 41:33.900
Here's the thing.

41:33.900 --> 41:35.400
From now on,

41:35.400 --> 41:37.600
please take good care of my wife.

41:37.630 --> 41:38.510
You know what?

41:38.510 --> 41:40.960
She'll join your sales department
in a few days.

41:40.960 --> 41:43.030
I think we should treat you to dinner.

41:43.030 --> 41:44.490
You have to do us the honor.

41:45.000 --> 41:46.000
Of course I'll take good care of her.

41:46.000 --> 41:46.960
It's no big deal.

41:47.440 --> 41:48.920
I'll ask Qian Xun to guide her.

41:48.920 --> 41:49.650
Thanks a lot.

41:50.070 --> 41:52.230
Not at all. We're old friends.

41:53.870 --> 41:55.000
I'll get going then.

41:56.550 --> 41:57.150
By the way...

41:57.150 --> 41:57.850
Um...

41:57.960 --> 41:59.070
How's it going with Kuanli?

41:59.070 --> 41:59.920
Is it confirmed?

41:59.920 --> 42:00.520
Yes, it is.

42:01.070 --> 42:01.960
After Purong is entrusted to Kuanli,

42:01.960 --> 42:03.190
it'll only earn more profits.

42:03.190 --> 42:04.840
Don't worry.
If your wife works in my hotel,

42:04.840 --> 42:06.030
she won't be at a disadvantage.

42:06.030 --> 42:07.190
-Okay, okay.
-Alright. I'm leaving.

42:07.190 --> 42:07.670
Alright.

42:07.670 --> 42:08.190
Thanks.

42:12.800 --> 42:13.670
Hello, welcome.

42:13.670 --> 42:14.280
How many people?

42:14.280 --> 42:14.810
Just one.

42:14.840 --> 42:16.170
Okay. This way, please.

42:16.280 --> 42:17.190
Mr. Ji?

42:18.630 --> 42:19.400
What a coincidence.

42:19.400 --> 42:21.280
-It's nice to see you here.
-Mr. Nie.

42:21.280 --> 42:23.480
Are you back from abroad for a vacation?

42:23.550 --> 42:24.840
I'm just taking a few days off.

42:24.840 --> 42:26.070
Have you received the email?

42:26.070 --> 42:27.110
Yes, I have.

42:27.110 --> 42:28.190
Thank you so much.

42:28.360 --> 42:29.710
Let me report it to you.

42:29.710 --> 42:31.110
We've already started working on

42:31.110 --> 42:32.230
the luxury wilderness desert route.

42:32.230 --> 42:33.480
The most critical thing now

42:33.480 --> 42:35.150
is to wait for you to resume work.

42:35.150 --> 42:36.410
And then we can sync up.

42:36.520 --> 42:37.550
No need to wait for me.

42:37.550 --> 42:39.340
I've alreday informed those several

42:39.340 --> 42:40.760
department directors below me.

42:40.760 --> 42:41.640
They'll fully cooperate

42:41.640 --> 42:43.400
with your proposal at any time.

42:43.400 --> 42:44.110
Thank you.

42:44.110 --> 42:45.240
Thank you very much.

42:45.320 --> 42:47.360
Are you here to eat?

42:48.070 --> 42:49.440
I'm just here to grab a quick bite.

42:49.440 --> 42:49.970
Look.

42:50.110 --> 42:51.360
There's no time like the present.

42:51.360 --> 42:53.030
This is a good chance for us
to have a meal together.

42:53.030 --> 42:54.110
A few colleagues of mine are here,

42:54.110 --> 42:55.510
so we can even have a chat.

42:55.960 --> 42:56.360
Okay.

42:56.670 --> 42:57.230
Let's go.

42:57.400 --> 42:58.030
Let's go.

42:58.030 --> 42:58.840
Come on.

42:58.840 --> 42:59.840
Take a small bite.

43:00.030 --> 43:02.760
You didn't expect
there would be so many people, did you?

43:02.760 --> 43:03.370
Mom.

43:03.760 --> 43:04.900
A friend of mine is here.

43:04.900 --> 43:05.980
My mom and dad.

43:06.070 --> 43:06.840
Hello, Mr. and Mrs. Nie.

43:06.840 --> 43:07.480
Hello.

43:07.480 --> 43:07.940
Come on.

43:09.150 --> 43:10.440
These are all my relatives.

43:10.440 --> 43:10.840
Okay.

43:10.840 --> 43:12.640
Let me introduce my colleagues.

43:12.840 --> 43:14.340
My assistant, Zhao Keqi.

43:14.630 --> 43:16.330
Feng Bin and Liu Minghui.

43:16.670 --> 43:17.150
Hello.

43:17.150 --> 43:17.630
Let me formally

43:17.630 --> 43:19.160
introduce this gentleman.

43:19.710 --> 43:21.200
Svelto Hotel Group,

43:21.590 --> 43:22.110
Ji Feng.

43:22.960 --> 43:24.210
Welcome!

43:25.320 --> 43:26.590
Mr. Ji.

43:27.380 --> 43:28.420
Here, Mr. Ji.

43:29.590 --> 43:30.840
Let me introduce myself first.

43:30.840 --> 43:33.630
I'm the director
of the HSKP Department of this hotel,

43:33.630 --> 43:34.910
Feng Kaixin.

43:35.280 --> 43:35.880
Mr. Feng.

43:36.630 --> 43:38.690
Mr. Ji, you're well-known overseas.

43:39.110 --> 43:40.360
As this is my first time meeting you,

43:40.360 --> 43:41.070
let me drink a toast to you.

43:41.070 --> 43:42.030
I'll drink it up first.

43:42.030 --> 43:43.030
You're already drinking.

43:43.030 --> 43:44.560
You haven't even eaten yet.

43:47.150 --> 43:47.820
You can really hold your liquor!

43:47.820 --> 43:48.590
Come on. Let me refill your glass.

43:48.590 --> 43:49.190
That's enough.

43:49.190 --> 43:50.110
You can drink later.

43:50.110 --> 43:51.040
What's the rush?

43:51.480 --> 43:52.940
Bring another chair here.

43:54.590 --> 43:55.320
This is my fault.

43:55.320 --> 43:56.400
I'll arrange it right away.

43:56.400 --> 43:57.150
Okay. Thank you.

43:57.150 --> 43:58.430
-Waiter.
-This way.

43:58.710 --> 43:59.360
Waiter!

43:59.380 --> 44:00.840
Why don't you take my seat?

44:01.150 --> 44:02.770
How can we let you
give your seat to the guest?

44:02.770 --> 44:04.230
Your health is important.

44:04.230 --> 44:05.190
It's okay.

44:06.110 --> 44:06.880
Who is this?

44:09.590 --> 44:11.110
My wife, Zhenzhen.

44:12.360 --> 44:14.070
I'm Lu Zhenzhen,

44:14.090 --> 44:15.050
Mr. Ji.

44:15.630 --> 44:16.320
Mrs. Nie.

44:17.710 --> 44:19.430
-Congratulations, Mr. Nie.
-Thank you.

44:19.430 --> 44:20.030
Sit.

44:20.320 --> 44:21.190
Coming.

44:22.360 --> 44:23.610
Just squeeze in.

44:23.880 --> 44:24.710
Um...

44:25.550 --> 44:26.360
I'm sorry.

44:26.840 --> 44:28.550
Let me explain it to you all.

44:28.630 --> 44:29.670
In this banquet hall,

44:29.670 --> 44:31.440
there are two wedding parties.

44:31.550 --> 44:33.250
The waiters have all gone to help.

44:33.250 --> 44:34.480
But it doesn't matter.

44:34.480 --> 44:36.610
I've arranged for an attendant
from our HSKP Department.

44:36.610 --> 44:37.800
She will be here shortly.

44:37.800 --> 44:39.030
Do the attendants from the HSKP Department

44:39.030 --> 44:40.690
know the restaurant's rules?

44:41.840 --> 44:43.110
I've transferred

44:43.150 --> 44:45.250
the best attendant
from our executive floor.

44:45.250 --> 44:45.960
She can learn fast.

44:45.960 --> 44:47.280
There will be absolutely no problem.

44:47.280 --> 44:48.230
I'm really sorry

44:48.230 --> 44:49.280
to cause you trouble.

44:49.280 --> 44:50.360
Not at all.

44:50.590 --> 44:51.760
Alright. Let's eat.

44:51.760 --> 44:52.820
Come on. Let's eat.

44:55.320 --> 44:57.510
Ask the attendant-on-duty
of the executive floor to come here now.

44:57.510 --> 44:58.000
Hurry up!
